30|$|As {{mentioned}} in the model description in the previous Sect. 4.4, the <b>additional</b> <b>holiday</b> dummy approach might be inappropriate for the fixed-date public holidays. However, this issue might be solved by combining the holiday as weekday approach (Sect. 4.3) with the <b>additional</b> <b>holiday</b> dummy methods (Sect. 4.4). So {{it is able to}} construct a model that joins the properties of both public holiday modeling approaches efficiently.|$|R
