30|$|The next {{class of}} models is the hybrid class {{containing}} <b>additional</b> weekday <b>holiday</b> dummies but replacing fixed-date holiday dummies. The representatives AdwhRpfh and AdwhRpfH show similar performance to the replacing methods. So {{it seems that}} replacing approach substantially improves the forecasting accuracy compared to the pure <b>additional</b> <b>holiday</b> dummy methodology. Still, the hybrid approach {{is not able to}} outperform the pure replacing holiday dummy method.|$|R
50|$|Emery Go-Round {{operates}} four fixed routes. Service operates daily, except selected holidays, {{with reduced}} service levels {{on weekends and}} selected <b>additional</b> <b>holidays.</b> All routes begin and end at MacArthur BART Station in Oakland.|$|E
